welcome_message_body: Welcome to Wylie, where small-town charm meets big-city amenities! Get ready to explore our quaint shops, delicious dining options, and beautiful parks. We hope you enjoy your time here!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Love Field Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Southwest Airlines Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is dedicated to Southwest Airlines, the largest carrier at Love Field Airport.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network for up to 2 hours.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Terrell Field Airport houses all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Terrell Field Airport handles all freight and cargo shipments.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Private Terminal
